<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://debconf12.debconf.org/\"><img src=\"http://blog.fcestrada.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/DebConf12-300x117.png\" title=\"DebConf 12\" height=\"117\" width=\"300\" alt=\"DebConf 12\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-176\" /></a></p>
